  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下教育系统的数据流转，特别是LMS门户、成绩同步和内容分发这几个核心模块的交互关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，我先确认一下结构。LMS门户是核心入口，成绩同步是独立服务，内容CDN作为子系统承载流量，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，但成绩同步不只是服务，它更像一个谈判中枢——LMS门户定义规则，课堂服务影响议价，还有约束条件叠加进来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把BARG作为核心节点，让DEF指向它标注'定义45%'，SOFT指向它标注'影响议价'，COMP也指向它标注'添加约束'。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "另外，学生数据库和LMS门户之间有个边界移动的关系，内容CDN对门户也有负载压力，这两个要体现出来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：GOV到VFI标注'转移边界'，DISC到VFI标注'增加负载'。学生数据库还要直接给LMS门户提供数据吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "需要，ABF到DEF是数据喂养关系。还有，成绩同步这个中枢要有反馈回路——它能重置LMS的规则，收紧对COMP的审计。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "添加了BARG到DEF的'重置规则'，BARG到COMP的'收紧审计'。那BARG和SOFT、GOV之间呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "BARG要扩展与课堂服务的交易，还要设定与学生数据库的集成条款。这两个都是输出方向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成，BARG到SOFT标注'扩展交易'，BARG到GOV标注'设定集成条款'。现在看CDN子系统内部，VFI和OUT之间怎么连？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "VFI有溢出需求到OUT，DISC和OUT之间还有个占用循环。OUT作为CDN子系统的出口，要承受媒体压力并反馈给POL。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已画：VFI到OUT的'溢出需求'，DISC到OUT的'占用循环'，OUT到POL的'媒体压力'。POL是内容CDN的另一个节点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，POL代表政策立场，它受媒体压力后会改变对BARG的态度，同时OUT在危机时也要直接响应BARG。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "添加了POL到BARG的'改变立场'，OUT到BARG的'危机响应'。还有条虚线关系，POL和DEF之间是叙事层面的关联？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，用虚线标注'narrative'，这是软约束。现在调整视觉层次：BARG、VFI、POL是核心，用primary样式；DEF、SOFT、COMP、GOV、DISC、ABF是支撑层。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_GradeSync",
